{"tid":1646511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"和理非其實大把嘢做 一人一片追擊保皇狗獨立狗！","createTime":"2019-10-11T10:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T10:47:09.000Z","uid":221265,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2f82bad8c61037d9002d7b58dc8ea6abd7ac3bf8","tid":1646511,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:26:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S8bbVyEJtrg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS8bbVyEJtrg&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=a45c5e89\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S8bbVyEJtrg</a><br />\n<br />\n區選又嚟<br />\n好撚多保皇狗扮獨立驚死人知佢哋親共(見片)<br />\n<br />\n區選個個區<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">年年成億資源 比晒啲保皇狗蛇齋餅稯箍票</span></strong><br />\n起埋晒啲垃圾地標 開埋晒啲BAD TASTE 老年向嘅乜燈會物晚會<br />\n<br />\n血債當然唔可能票償<br />\n但難得班保皇狗假獨立狗為咗選票出晒街扮晒為民請命拉票<br />\n<br />\n依個時候唔問佢點睇警暴(盡量問得SPECIFIC啲，最好問埋當區警暴)，<br />\n點睇啲私人屋苑任警察入/唔俾警察入就拉<br />\n點睇區會之前開親 民主派想譴責同跟進警暴都俾保皇狗擋晒<br />\n<br />\n真係大把令佢哋出醜機會<br />\n<br />\n記得<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一片  問到佢哋出撚晒醜</span></span></strong><br />\n但唔好掂到佢哋呀 佢哋又會話我哋想暴力影響選舉<br />\n之後又話要拉倒個選舉㗎啦(雖然我諗林鄭實會咁做)<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得之前有民主派素人小花落區比人打後腦？<br />\n對家雖然咁仆街<br />\n<br />\n我地和理非基數大，私私文文影下片 同佢宣傳下<br />\n<br />\n又多啲新TALKING POINT 同個運動增加下燃料啦！"},{"pid":"68dd547038d2302b4d6373c64fc5371d977972a1","tid":1646511,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"80bdd928173ca70b44eb3c5a21ad6aac2e9a7653","tid":1646511,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:30:43.000Z","msg":"嘩原來仲要喺FB刪人哋留言真係嘔心"},{"pid":"302c9dae3d1a6f77ba4844f746169468f3824bf8","tid":1646511,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:32:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34a022680441e30860de2660f65a6e0be6024f03","tid":1646511,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:32:49.000Z","msg":"大家要做㗎真係<br />\n個個區都做<br />\n<br />\n散晒入啲FB / WHATSAPP GROUP"},{"pid":"9b0054852a0356c613059a88cf697df758ea805e","tid":1646511,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:33:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保護前線 刻不容緩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人，我哋眾籌咗好多次，賣廣告、出書、拍電影&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n但係最重要嘅，係買裝備保護前線!!!!<br />\n而唔係等佢哋受傷咗之後先去支援佢地!!!<br />\n<br />\n請大家快啲支持YHF！過咗一日，先得十幾人支持，好傷心<br />\n係，我無Fact check，但係我情願相信，呢個世界有人願意冒被捕風險，都要做眾籌<br />\n希望大家衡量過後，可以支持做實事嘅團隊。<br />\n件事未完，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輸贏都好，保護手足應該係和理非最需要關心嘅事。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1643523/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1643523/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/payments/?oid=1662043&amp;err=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fpayments%2F%3Foid%3D1662043%26err%3D1&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=ff696314\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/payments/?oid=1662043&amp;err=1</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TJhHcCt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTJhHcCt.jpg&h=5bcbfa54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c30765203c3f6717a7b73d8e9e7ec061aa432223","tid":1646511,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"[置頂]仲做浮屍推理？集氣搵佢男朋友或友人出黎好過啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1645581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1645581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n屌 我無用呀 要推撚到識佢嘅人先有方法搵到真相呀<br />\n9推理真係無用架...<br />\n推上去呀 再唔搵人就連唯一線索都會被消失"},{"pid":"539d04021d75a626030ac1f710756ecd1d319f61","tid":1646511,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c30765203c3f6717a7b73d8e9e7ec061aa432223","tid":1646511,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT